      "writtenOn": "2026-03-24T08:32:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e I would also document this either in the build.md which is easier to discover than this commit message.\n\nThis has been done already.\n\n\u003e Or even better document this in a new section \"bazel mod build for plugins\" in the plugin developer guide (https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/Documentation/dev-plugins.html) and reference it from the plugin\u0027s build.md. This would help to avoid duplicate documentation in all the plugins which will migrate to a bazel mod build.\n\nIt can be addressed in a follow-up change, together with a change in Gerrit\u0027s documentation.",
