      "writtenOn": "2026-03-24T09:53:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e Or even better document this in a new section \"bazel mod build for plugins\" in the plugin developer guide (https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/Documentation/dev-plugins.html) \n\nGood point. We already have dedicated documentation for building plugins, which was expanded as part of the recent Bazel modules migration series, see: [1].\n\nParticularly, it\u0027s documented how to create both lock files:\n\n```\n  $ bazelisk run @oauth_plugin_deps//:pin\n```\n\nand\n\n```\n  $ bazelisk mod deps --lockfile_mode\u003dupdate\n```\n\n[1]: https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/Documentation/dev-build-plugins.html#_plugins_with_external_dependencies",
